### Speech-to-Text OpenAI API Testing

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/speech/health
Accept: application/json

### Transcribe Resource File (Legacy endpoint)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/speech/resource

### Transcribe Resource File (New endpoint)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/speech/transcribe/resource
Accept: application/json

### Transcribe Resource File with custom filename
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/speech/transcribe/resource?filename=speech-1760589387683.mp3
Accept: application/json

### Upload and Transcribe Audio File
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/speech/transcribe
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="audio.mp3"
Content-Type: audio/mpeg

< /path/to/your/audio/file.mp3
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="language"

en
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="responseFormat"

json
--boundary--

### Upload and Transcribe Audio File (Async)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/speech/transcribe/async
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="audio.mp3"
Content-Type: audio/mpeg

< /path/to/your/audio/file.mp3
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="language"

en
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="responseFormat"

verbose_json
--boundary--

### Check Actuator Health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### Check Actuator Metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Check Specific Metric (transcription requests)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/transcription.requests.total
Accept: application/json

### Check Prometheus Metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/prometheus
Accept: text/plain

